description: A funny dad joke about milk in a carton.
title: Milk in a Carton
n_1: Dad is at the grocery store checkout with a carton of milk.
c1_1: Can you put the milk in a bag?
c2_1: Sure, would you like the milk in a bag?
n_2: The cashier starts to put the milk in a bag.
c1_2: No, just leave it in the carton!
n_3: Both Dad and the cashier laugh at the joke.
n_4: They finish the transaction with smiles.
